; Regression test for #620: -j should output values in a consistent base
; unit for plotting.  Without this fix, quantity() would return values in
; different unreduced units (e.g. hours vs minutes), making them
; incomparable for graphing tools.

i 2023/01/01 08:00:00 Project:A
o 2023/01/01 10:00:00
i 2023/01/01 14:00:00 Project:B
o 2023/01/01 14:30:00

test reg -j
2023-01-01 7200
2023-01-01 1800
end test

test reg -J
2023-01-01 7200
2023-01-01 9000
end test
